⍝ Multi-line program storage
⍝ Tests [N] line entry, )LIST, )RUN, )ERASE
⍝ NOTE: This sample is for documentation only.
⍝ COR24 emulator testing uses --uart-input with ASCII syntax.
⍝
⍝ Example COR24 session:
⍝   [1] N ← 1
⍝   [2] N
⍝   [3] N ← N + 1
⍝   [4] →(N−6)/2
⍝   )LIST
⍝   )RUN
⍝ Expected output: 1 2 3 4 5
